{"version":1,"entries":{"person_1306832_translations":{"at":1772689444279,"data":{"id":1306832,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Sarah Lee","primary":true}}]}},"person_587490_translations":{"at":1772689450553,"data":{"id":587490,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"錢國偉","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Wilson Chin Kwok-Wai was born on April 9, 1962 in Hong Kong, British Crown Colony. He was a director and actor, known for Kidnap Ding Ding Don, Special Female Force and Lan Kwai Fong. He was married to Calinda Chan. He died on October 27, 2020 in Hong Kong.","name":"Wilson Chin Kwok-Wai","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"錢國偉","primary":false}}]}},"person_1850227_translations":{"at":1772689451874,"data":{"id":1850227,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"郑合惠子，1994年出生于福建省福州市，中国内地影视女演员。\n\n2013年，从福州延安中学毕业的郑合惠子考入了北京现代音乐学院播音主持系。\n\n2014年，郑合惠子在第六届“北音之音”校园主持人选拔大赛上被特聘为了团委年度舞台专属主持人；同年，她还与同学们共同出演了北音与万合天宜联合制作的网络微电影《僵小尸》（又名《嗜血僵尸》）。\n\n2015年，大二在读的郑合惠子被万合天宜看中成为旗下签约艺人，并正式开始了个人的演艺生涯；同年，郑合惠子因出演古装喜剧《名侦探狄仁杰》而获得颇高人气。","name":"郑合惠子","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zheng Hehuizi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"鄭合惠子，福建省福州市人，中華人民共和國女演員、萬合天宜簽約藝人，北京現代音樂研修學院影視戲劇學院播音主持系2017屆畢業生。","name":"鄭合惠子","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Чжэн Хэ Хуэй Цзы","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","engl